                    </td>
                    <td class="border border-gray-200 px-2 py-1">30° – 37°</td>
                    <td class="border border-gray-200 px-2 py-1">58% – 75%</td>
                    <td class="border border-gray-200 px-2 py-1">
                      Steeper roofs, better snow shedding
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
